rows.label: qst610102_msg0001
rows.name:
Huh? Oh, Eric's got you
hunting down the thieves?

rows.label: qst610102_msg0002
rows.name:
I've not seen anyone, but I
might know something useful.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, it's just some gossip
I heard from my husband.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0004
rows.name:
Ever been to a place called Seigle
Fell? You know, down near the rear
end of the Gula Divine Beast.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, I bet you didn't know
there's a little hut by the
waterfall, did you?

rows.label: qst610102_msg0006
rows.name:
My husband says he saw a pretty
big stash of lumber down there.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0007
rows.name:
Which is weird, because nobody's supposed
to be living there, you know? Sounds
a tad suspicious if you ask me.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0008
rows.name:
Might be nothing, but
might be something.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0009
rows.name: At any rate, that's all I know.

rows.label: qst610102_msg0010
rows.name:
Hope it comes in useful. And
good luck on your hunt!
